data.title: Managing Oracle Coherence
data.meta_description:
Managing Oracle Coherence - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides information about managing Oracle Coherence clusters. It discusses using JMX and REST for management. It also covers registering custom MBeans and using Coherence metrics.

The document is divided into chapters that cover: 1) an introduction to Coherence management, 2) using JMX to manage clusters, 3) registering custom MBeans, and 4) using Coherence metrics. It provides information on configuring and accessing management features for monitoring and administration of Coherence clusters.
